latestPosts.caption:
How it began 💛🌼 

Thank you to @preetyali @imtiazaliofficial @idaali11 for hosting the most beautiful haldi ceremony for us 🥹🙏🏼

𝗧𝗧 𝗕𝗥𝗜𝗗𝗘 𝗔𝗡𝗗 𝗚𝗥𝗢𝗢𝗠 - 𝗔𝗔𝗟𝗜𝗬𝗔𝗛 𝗞𝗔𝗦𝗛𝗬𝗔𝗣 & 𝗦𝗛𝗔𝗡𝗘 𝗚𝗥𝗘𝗚𝗢𝗜𝗥𝗘

When we met Aaliyah Kashyap (@aaliyahkashyap) and Shane Gregoire (@shanegregoire) , their exuberance shone through and we knew we had to craft for them something that let their inner light shine. We celebrate their love with timeless artistry and intricate craftsmanship on their wedding day.

Aaliyah stuns in our Bloom Couture lehenga, featuring a lace-embroidered jaal enriched with blooming floral hues, detailed kasab work, and intricate zardozi accents. The scalloped lace border on the hem and the signature trail are beautifully complemented by a statement TT blouse and a delicate drape adorned with 3D floral highlights.

Shane, looks ever charming in our classic TT sherwani, showcasing intricate multi-coloured silk thread embroidery, embellished with pearls and sequins.

We wish both Aaliyah and Shane a harmonious and joyful union.

Stylist: @sheefajgilani 

#TarunTahiliani #TTBride #TTGroom
